*Saznali* smo da će biti snega u noći. (We found out that it will snow at night.)

Susretli smo se sa ljudima koji su nam *saznali* šta se događa. (We met people who told us what was happening.)

Nismo *saznali* kako da se postavimo na najbolji način. (We didn't find out how to position ourselves in the best way.)

*Saznali* smo da je ona otišla u inostranstvo. (We found out that she had gone abroad.)

Oni su *saznali* da će dobiti novac. (They found out that they will get money.)